{
  "name": "NeoTravel v2 — Lead → Qualification → Devis → CRM → Relance",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "neotravel-lead",
        "responseMode": "responseNode",
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [250, 300],
      "id": "node-webhook",
      "name": "Webhook NeoTravel Lead",
      "webhookId": "neotravel-lead"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "Tu es l'assistant commercial de NeoTravel, spécialiste du transport de groupe en autocar. Tu analyses les demandes prospects et extrais les informations en JSON structuré.\n\nRÈGLES ABSOLUES :\n- Tu ne calcules JAMAIS un prix\n- Tu ne proposes JAMAIS de remise ou condition commerciale\n- Tu réponds UNIQUEMENT en JSON valide\n\nChamps obligatoires à extraire :\n- nom_societe (string)\n- email (string, email valide)\n- telephone (string)\n- ville_depart (string)\n- ville_arrivee (string)\n- date_depart (string, format YYYY-MM-DD)\n- nb_passagers (integer > 0 et <= 85)\n- distance_km (integer > 0)\n- aller_retour (boolean)\n- urgence (string: DD_PRIORITAIRE si départ < 48h, DD_URGENT si < 7 jours, DD_NORMAL si < 3 mois, DD_3MOISETPLUS sinon)\n\nCAS D'ESCALADE HUMAINE (retourner statut: cas_complexe) :\n- Trajet international ou multi-étapes\n- Voyage > 3 jours avec nuits chauffeur\n- Demande de remise ou condition sur mesure\n- nb_passagers > 75\n- Données incohérentes ou ambiguës\n\nSi champs manquants : {statut: incomplet, champs_manquants: [liste], message: message poli au prospect}\nSi cas complexe : {statut: cas_complexe, raison: explication, resume: résumé pour le commercial}\nSi complet et standard : {statut: complet, donnees: {...tous les champs...}}"
        }
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 1.7,
      "position": [500, 300],
      "id": "node-ai-agent",
      "name": "AI Agent"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rules": {
          "values": [
            {
              "conditions": {
                "options": {
                  "caseSensitive": true,
                  "leftValue": "",
                  "typeValidation": "strict"
                },
                "conditions": [
                  {
                    "id": "rule-complet",
                    "leftValue": "={{ $json.statut }}",
                    "rightValue": "complet",
                    "operator": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "operation": "equals"
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "combinator": "and"
              },
              "renameOutput": true,
              "outputKey": "complet"
            },
            {
              "conditions": {
                "options": {
                  "caseSensitive": true,
                  "leftValue": "",
                  "typeValidation": "strict"
                },
                "conditions": [
                  {
                    "id": "rule-incomplet",
                    "leftValue": "={{ $json.statut }}",
                    "rightValue": "incomplet",
                    "operator": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "operation": "equals"
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "combinator": "and"
              },
              "renameOutput": true,
              "outputKey": "incomplet"
            },
            {
              "conditions": {
                "options": {
                  "caseSensitive": true,
                  "leftValue": "",
                  "typeValidation": "strict"
                },
                "conditions": [
                  {
                    "id": "rule-cas-complexe",
                    "leftValue": "={{ $json.statut }}",
                    "rightValue": "cas_complexe",
                    "operator": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "operation": "equals"
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "combinator": "and"
              },
              "renameOutput": true,
              "outputKey": "cas_complexe"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {
          "fallbackOutput": "extra"
        }
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.switch",
      "typeVersion": 3.2,
      "position": [750, 300],
      "id": "node-switch",
      "name": "Router Statut"
    },

    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "https://neotravel.vercel.app/api/devis",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "Content-Type",
              "value": "application/json"
            }
          ]
        },
        "sendBody": true,
        "specifyBody": "json",
        "jsonBody": "={{ JSON.stringify($node[\"AI Agent\"].json.donnees) }}",
        "options": {
          "timeout": 10000
        }
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [1000, 100],
      "id": "node-http-devis",
      "name": "Calculer Devis"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "create",
        "base": {
          "__rl": true,
          "value": "appGGAlQWuG2wb5kd",
          "mode": "id"
        },
        "table": {
          "__rl": true,
          "value": "tblZivQRw7GW1jawF",
          "mode": "id"
        },
        "columns": {
          "mappingMode": "defineBelow",
          "value": {
            "nom_societe": "={{ $node[\"AI Agent\"].json.donnees.nom_societe }}",
            "email": "={{ $node[\"AI Agent\"].json.donnees.email }}",
            "telephone": "={{ $node[\"AI Agent\"].json.donnees.telephone }}",
            "ville_depart": "={{ $node[\"AI Agent\"].json.donnees.ville_depart }}",
            "ville_arrivee": "={{ $node[\"AI Agent\"].json.donnees.ville_arrivee }}",
            "date_depart": "={{ $node[\"AI Agent\"].json.donnees.date_depart }}",
            "nb_passagers": "={{ $node[\"AI Agent\"].json.donnees.nb_passagers }}",
            "distance_km": "={{ $node[\"AI Agent\"].json.donnees.distance_km }}",
            "aller_retour": "={{ $node[\"AI Agent\"].json.donnees.aller_retour }}",
            "urgence": "={{ $node[\"AI Agent\"].json.donnees.urgence }}",
            "prix_ht": "={{ $node[\"Calculer Devis\"].json.prix_ht }}",
            "prix_ttc": "={{ $node[\"Calculer Devis\"].json.prix_ttc }}",
            "statut": "Qualifié"
          }
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.airtable",
      "typeVersion": 2.1,
      "position": [1250, 100],
      "id": "node-airtable-demande",
      "name": "CRM Créer Demande"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "create",
        "base": {
          "__rl": true,
          "value": "appGGAlQWuG2wb5kd",
          "mode": "id"
        },
        "table": {
          "__rl": true,
          "value": "tblv2r0FCkW1SUYtK",
          "mode": "id"
        },
        "columns": {
          "mappingMode": "defineBelow",
          "value": {
            "nom_societe": "={{ $node[\"AI Agent\"].json.donnees.nom_societe }}",
            "email": "={{ $node[\"AI Agent\"].json.donnees.email }}",
            "prix_ht": "={{ $node[\"Calculer Devis\"].json.prix_ht }}",
            "tva": "={{ $node[\"Calculer Devis\"].json.tva }}",
            "prix_ttc": "={{ $node[\"Calculer Devis\"].json.prix_ttc }}",
            "detail_calcul": "={{ JSON.stringify($node[\"Calculer Devis\"].json.lignes) }}",
            "coefficients": "={{ JSON.stringify($node[\"Calculer Devis\"].json.coefficients) }}",
            "statut_devis": "Généré"
          }
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.airtable",
      "typeVersion": 2.1,
      "position": [1500, 100],
      "id": "node-airtable-devis",
      "name": "CRM Créer Devis"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "fromEmail": "devis@neotravel.fr",
        "toEmail": "={{ $node[\"AI Agent\"].json.donnees.email }}",
        "subject": "Votre devis NeoTravel — {{ $node[\"AI Agent\"].json.donnees.nom_societe }}",
        "html": "<h2>Bonjour,</h2><p>Merci pour votre demande auprès de NeoTravel. Voici votre devis personnalisé :</p><table style=\"border-collapse:collapse;width:100%;max-width:500px\"><tr style=\"background:#f5f5f5\"><td style=\"padding:8px;border:1px solid #ddd\"><strong>Trajet</strong></td><td style=\"padding:8px;border:1px solid #ddd\">{{ $node[\"AI Agent\"].json.donnees.ville_depart }} → {{ $node[\"AI Agent\"].json.donnees.ville_arrivee }}</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:8px;border:1px solid #ddd\"><strong>Date</strong></td><td style=\"padding:8px;border:1px solid #ddd\">{{ $node[\"AI Agent\"].json.donnees.date_depart }}</td></tr><tr style=\"background:#f5f5f5\"><td style=\"padding:8px;border:1px solid #ddd\"><strong>Passagers</strong></td><td style=\"padding:8px;border:1px solid #ddd\">{{ $node[\"AI Agent\"].json.donnees.nb_passagers }}</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:8px;border:1px solid #ddd\"><strong>Distance</strong></td><td style=\"padding:8px;border:1px solid #ddd\">{{ $node[\"AI Agent\"].json.donnees.distance_km }} km{{ $node[\"AI Agent\"].json.donnees.aller_retour ? ' (aller/retour)' : ' (aller simple)' }}</td></tr><tr style=\"background:#f5f5f5\"><td style=\"padding:8px;border:1px solid #ddd\"><strong>Prix HT</strong></td><td style=\"padding:8px;border:1px solid #ddd\">{{ $node[\"Calculer Devis\"].json.prix_ht }} €</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:8px;border:1px solid #ddd\"><strong>TVA (10%)</strong></td><td style=\"padding:8px;border:1px solid #ddd\">{{ $node[\"Calculer Devis\"].json.tva }} €</td></tr><tr style=\"background:#2563eb;color:white\"><td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #ddd\"><strong>Prix TTC</strong></td><td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #ddd\"><strong>{{ $node[\"Calculer Devis\"].json.prix_ttc }} €</strong></td></tr></table><p style=\"margin-top:20px\">Ce devis est valable 30 jours. Pour confirmer ou poser vos questions, répondez directement à cet email.</p><p>À bientôt,<br/><strong>L'équipe NeoTravel</strong></p>"
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.resend",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [1750, 100],
      "id": "node-email-devis",
      "name": "Envoyer Devis Email",
      "credentials": {
